org.harctoolbox.lirc

Class LircConfigFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.harctoolbox.lirc.LircConfigFile

  • public final class LircConfigFile
extends Object
    This class parses the Lircd configuration file(s). Its preferred public members are the static functions parseConfig, updating a Map of LircRemotes, while guaranteeing that all remotes will be presentm possibly with modified keys for satisfying the uniqueness requirement.
